behaviour:
Gaz'haragoth fights his opponents in close combat.

Gaz'haragoth has many announced abilities:
*{{Sound|Gaz'haragoth begins to channel DEATH AND DOOM into the area! RUN!}} - Announced rarely. Five seconds after being announced, Gaz'haragoth will cast his ultimate attack. This attack is insanely strong and will kill almost anyone (it always deals 30,000 [[Energy Damage]]). When he casts it, there will be another announcement: {{Sound|Gaz'haragoth calls down: DEATH AND DOOM!}}
*{{Sound|Chill out!}} - Announced very often. When announced, Gaz'haragoth casts his [[Ice Damage|Ice]] UE which deals 1000 damage.
*{{Sound|Minions! Follow my call!}} - Announced every time he is hit if he is not at his summon capacity. When he announces this, Gaz'haragoth will attempt to summon up to 2 [[Minion of Gaz'haragoth|Minions of Gaz'haragoth]]. It will fail if Gaz'haragoth has no room to summon.
*{{Sound|Gaz'haragoth beginns to draw on the nightmares to HEAL himself!}} - In about 8 seconds Gaz'haragoth will heal himself for 300,000. When he does, another message is announced: {{Sound|Gaz'haragoth HEALS himself!}}
